parcel.description: Does Lexx's Vision have anything to do with The Cult of the Eye? Or is it mere coincidence? Eyes try to fly up, but are chained to the ground. Some escaped, but only as angels. Passed away African American heroes and others huddle together with halos. Text reads, "vision without courage is sterile", "all vision suffers blind spots", and "ay! foreign eye leaves everyone blind". The center feature is a hand reaching out to show Delta over Time. Ancient kemetian symbols, flowers, and figures abound
parcel.name: VoxCon Lexx's Vision
parcel.label: park
